data.description:
Welcome to the perfect balance of peace, quiet and entertainment!  Two blocks away from the many festivals of historic downtown Guthrie, this remodeled modern farmhouse is your own private sanctuary that can be converted to party central at a moment's notice.  The exterior porches and unique floor plan combine the modern open farmhouse kitchen & living room combo with the privacy of secluded bedrooms deeper into the house.  The private alley and detached garage allow for plenty of front & rear guest parking options. Also less than 2 miles away from food, coffee, splash pads, walking trails, ponds, and schools.   Conveniently near I35 and Hwy 33 for rapid commute.  **AS-IS shortsale, subject to lender approval**

The home has several unique non-obvious features that add to the value of the property and will appeal strongly to buyers.   The seller is focused on a quick, fair & smooth transaction.  Call today to get the back story and schedule your private showing!
